The paper discusses the development of effective knowledge discovery techniques, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The task of singling out anomalous individuals is related to data mining and outlier detection, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the computational complexity of outlier detection problems, which is a common topic in cryptography (cs.CR) and algorithms (cs.DS).
